														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4812493">
									

<p>I'm sad to see it doesn't look like any of my critique was meaningfully applied - the only significant change I see is in the third addendum with the Archivist Prime stuff, and the language of that made it impossible to take seriously even before you threw the Zalgo in.</p>
<p>I'm still intrigued by the idea of something consuming First and the presentation is very nice but I maintain my critique that the Big Bad isn't communicated here well enough to be scary or effective.</p>

